reviews.review_text: Blessed Be ! Thanks For Poppin' This One Out. I Was Probably 20 Feet From Ya'. Watchin' The Alien Lightning Ships Come Over The Hill To Pause And Listen In With Us. This One's Closest To What I Heard. And Vocal Wise So Far Tops Of Whats Out On IA. A Very Special Show. An Audience Matrix Might Be Interesting To Anyone So Capable. This Offering Has The Hot Vocals That Are Missing From So Many Of The Others. If Any Might Be So Inclined. Calling Hunter Seamons.
